<p><strong>Q: Is signing up or subscription required for making purchases ?</strong></p>
<p><strong>A: <span class="details">Not required.</span></strong> <span class="unnamed1">You 
  are most welcome to go around and shop on our site without signing up ( also 
  referred to as subscription). However you may wish to avail the benefits of 
  signing up listed below.</span></p>
<p><strong>Q: Why Subscribe or sign up ?</strong></p>
<p> <strong>A: <span class="details">With signing up you get the following </span>: 
  </strong></p>
<ul>
  <li class="unnamed1">Monthly notification through email or post on new items.</li>
  <li class="unnamed1">Along with the notification great genuine discount offers</li>
  <li> <span class="unnamed1"><a name="wishlist"></a>A wish list feature. Each 
    subscriber has his own wish list. This list </span><span class="unnamed1"> 
    is useful in case you want to put off buying an item to a later date or the 
    item is out of stock. You can view the items in your wish list the next time 
    you visit the site making your search easy. In case the item is out of stock 
    we stock it up with a high priority. As and when the item is in stock you 
    will be automatically informed using your email id. Please note that <strong>you 
    are under no obligation to purchase</strong> or make any payment whatsoever 
    for the item.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Q: What are your obligations as a subscriber ?</strong></p>
<p><strong>A: <span class="details">Not much.</span></strong><span class="details"> 
  </span>As a subscriber your only obligations are the following:</p>
<ul>
  <li class="unnamed1">Your email id must be valid. In case the email id account 
    is discovered to be dysfunctional the discounts offered will be revoked.</li>
  <li class="unnamed1">As and when you make a purchase your purchases must be 
    of a minimum USD $10.00 (After applying discount but after adding handling 
    charges if any).</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Q: How does one subscribe ?</strong></p>
<p> <strong>A: <span class="details">Subscription or signing up is a single step 
  procedure.</span></strong> <span class="unnamed1">You sign up by providing us 
  your contact address (postal and email) and setting up a password. This email 
  and address are then used by us to contact you from time to time. We do not 
  send you mail more than twice a month, and mostly only once a month. The postal 
  address is useful for quick processing of the shipment. The email is <strong>not 
  provided</strong> to any third party. Click here to <a href="subscribe.cfm">sign-up</a> 
  now.</span></p>
